data.description: Very nicely uploaded NE Ranch with 3BD, 1 BA, 1375sf on main level sitting on almost an acre with three parcels totaling .78 of an acre and full Basement with an additional 1075sf. All new waterproof vinyl plank flooring in the hall and huge Living Room with wall of windows and natural light galore! Step down to the eat-in Kitchen with beautiful cabinetry,tile backsplash, breakfast bar, Dining Area, and corner pantry for plenty of storage! All the Bedrooms have brand new carpet and large closets! Primary Bedroom is spacious with walk-in closet/ versatile sitting/dressing room. Big Hall Bathroom with tub/shower combo with built-ins and storage shelving above the toilet! The Basement has Laundry hook ups and Bonus spaces perfect for a Rec Room/ Family Room/ Home Office or possibly a 4th BD! Pool table stays! Fully fenced back yard! Detached Garage has a nice workshop area! Gas forced air and central air! Walking distance to shopping and restaurants! Don't miss this one!
